.TH AI-PLAYBOOK-SEARCH 1 "" "ai-playbook" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
ai\-playbook\-search \- Search saved playbooks by substring
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBai\-playbook\fR search <query> [\-\-format human|fuzzy\-data\-source|json]
.SH DESCRIPTION
search filters the store by substring match against <query> and prints the
matches. Its human table carries the same LAST RUN column as list.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-format\fR \fI<fmt>\fR
output format: human|fuzzy\-data\-source|json
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
ai\-playbook search deploy
.fi
.SH "SEE ALSO"
\fBai\-playbook\fR(1)
